# Voraussetzungen
python installiert

1. esp tool installieren:

pip install esptool

2. Treiber installieren

https://www.silabs.com/developers/usb-to-uart-bridge-vcp-drivers

3. While holding down the “BOOT/FLASH” button, run the following command to erase the ESP32 flash memory:
esptool.py --chip esp32 erase_flash

4. Firmware installieren

esptool.py --chip esp32 --port com3 write_flash -z 0x1000 .\esp32\firmware\esp32-idf4-20210202-v1.14.bin

5. ampy installieren

pip install ampy

6. boot.py kopieren

ampy --port com3 put esp32/files/boot.py

7. IP-Adresse herausfinden:

import network
sta_if = network.WLAN(network.STA_IF)
print('network config:', sta_if.ifconfig())

8. Liberies installieren

import upip
upip.install('picoweb')
upip.install('pycopy-ulogging')

9. Dateien verschieben

ampy --port com3 put .\esp32\files\functions.py






